OL,6,     Gregion of Asturias on Spain's
OL,7,     Gnorth coast, winding through
OL,8,     Gmountains to a traditional
OL,9,     Gfiesta, exploring the capital
OL,10,     GOviedo, and sampling cloudy cider.
